### user login  
// leave a line after content type if not you will get an err header name must be valid
POST http://localhost:4000/user-api/auth
Content-Type: application/json  

{
    "email":"bhanu@gmail.com",
    "password":"bhanu"
} 

### Create new user
POST http://localhost:4000/user-api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "username":"bhanu",
    "password":"bhanu",
    "email":"bhanu@gmail.com",
    "age":24
}

###Update the existing user
