// Products api 
### reading all the products


### adding a new product
POST http://localhost:4000/product-api/product
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "productId":4,
    "productName":"pen",
    "price":15000,
    "brand":"camlin"
}

### read all product by brand
GET http://localhost:4000/product-api/product

### read all product by brand
GET http://localhost:4000/product-api/product/4


### updating a product
PUT http://localhost:4000/product-api/product/4
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "productId":4,
    "productName":"eraser",
    "price":30000,
    "brand":"apsara"
}

### deleteing an existing product by id
DELETE http://localhost:4000/product-api/product/4